<h1 style="color: #1B3B6F;">New User Signup</h1>

<p>A new user has registered on <strong>TourneyPing</strong>.</p>

<table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; background-color: #fff;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd; background-color: #f8f9fa; font-weight: bold; width: 120px;">Email</td>
    <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><%= @user.email %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd; background-color: #f8f9fa; font-weight: bold;">Signed up at</td>
    <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><%= @user.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p %Z") %></td>
  </tr>
</table>

<hr style="margin: 30px 0;">

<p style="color: #666; font-size: 12px;">
  This is an automated notification from TourneyPing.
</p>
